+- **Component:** `SampleAuxInfoReader` constructor (HEIF sequences-track parsing)
+- **CWE:** CWE-125 (Out-of-bounds Read)
+- **Issue:** The constructor iterates over `saiz->get_num_samples()` samples without validating that the count is consistent with the number of entries in the track's `chunks` vector. A crafted sequence file whose `saiz` box declares more samples than the chunk table covers advances `current_chunk` past `chunks.size()`, causing an out-of-bounds read.
